      <div class="doctor-card reveal" data-specialty="ortho" data-hospital="spine">
        <div class="doctor-photo"><div class="doctor-photo-placeholder" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#EFF6FF,#DBEAFE)"><Icon name="fa6-solid:user-doctor" style="color:#2554A0" /></div><div class="doctor-specialty-badge" style="background:#2554A0">กระดูกและข้อ</div></div>
        <div class="doctor-name">นพ. ศริษฏ์ หงษ์วิไล</div>
        <div class="doctor-title">ศัลยแพทย์กระดูกและข้อ</div>
        <div class="doctor-hospital"><Icon name="fa6-solid:hospital" /> MediThai สมองและกระดูก</div>
        <div class="doctor-tags"><span class="doctor-tag">Robotic UKA</span><span class="doctor-tag">Joint Replacement</span></div>
